i-MSCP Monitorix plugin ChangeLog
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.8
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Monitorix CGI binary must be run indirectly for partitions which are mounted with the noexec option

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.7
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Cronjob file path

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Path to monitorix.conf
	Fixed: Url for graphics creation
	Added: New parameter in config.php to enable graphs

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Plugin is not compatible with monitorix 3.5.0

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Plugin is not compatible with Perl version from Squeeze

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Updated according new plugin API (0.2.4)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Updated according new plugin API (0.2.0)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	First Release
